
Static Keyword:

	It refers to the common properties of all objects. 
	It can be applied with variables, blocks, class and methods.



-----------------------------------------------------------------	

Final Keyword

	- Can be used with Variable, Method and Class.

Final Variable: Final Variable means the value can't be modified in future.



-----------------------------------

Blank Final Variable: Blank Final Variable is not initialize at the time of declaration. It can be intialize only in constructor.

Static Blank Final Variable: Static Blank Final Variable can be initialize in static block only.

Final Method: Final Method can't be overridden in child class.

Final Class: If you declare any class final, no other class can extend it.
	
	
